{"tid":1403944,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8月4號將軍澳反送中 逃生路線補充","createTime":"2019-08-04T01:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T03:23:09.000Z","uid":240278,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4b2f452fc3a796f315539a67172fd895b10e9196","tid":1403944,"uid":240278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:15:58.000Z","msg":"黎緊下午就會有集會 雖然已經有人討論過點樣撤退<br />\n但係我視測完將軍澳之後 有少少補充 請大家去之前可以睇一睇<br />\n<br />\n係睇之前希望各位先睇左呢條Link 會好D<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1394216/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1394216/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n個人認為 將軍澳其實位置相較黎講比較偏僻<br />\n逃走既路線既位置其實萬變不離其中<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3egOE9k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3egOE9k.jpg&h=ff2fd2d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n主要係 <span style=\"color: red;\">調景嶺</span>、<span style=\"color: red;\">西貢</span>、同埋<span style=\"color: red;\">翠林</span>村 三個方向<br />\n而<span style=\"color: red;\">工業村其實係一個死路</span>，可以入去出唔翻 所以<span style=\"color: red;\">極度唔建議係果到出</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">清水灣方向</span>雖然有巴打提出過 但係同時亦有巴打擔心<span style=\"color: red;\">呢條路消耗既體力過大</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">容易被警察守株待兔</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">調景嶺方向</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UbYdRmf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUbYdRmf.jpg&h=df2f62a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果要係調景嶺成功撤退 個人認為有兩個條件<br />\n第一 交通要順暢 有巴士甚至地鐵可以出去<br />\n第二 警察唔會係封調景嶺<br />\n<br />\n如果我係警察 我會直接封鎖調景嶺 因為 調景嶺係將軍澳既交通匯集處 自然會比較多車可以出去 封鎖左會大大減少示威者既退路<br />\n<br />\n如果各位真係決定要行調景嶺方向有少少野要注意<br />\n調景嶺其實<span style=\"color: red;\">可以經華人墳場出去鯉魚門</span> 但係其路程比較遠<br />\n再加上如果你唔太識路既話 <br />\n你<span style=\"color: red;\">可能需要係調景嶺轉乘其他交通工具</span><br />\n變相你可能需要要早D 換好衫 以便偽裝成當地居民<br />\n<br />\n調景嶺有<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>知專學院</strong></span> 如有朋友同需要<span style=\"color: red;\"> 可以暫時躲藏於學校入面</span><br />\n當中 <span style=\"color: red;\">唐明街同寶邑路(1號同2號位)係大路黎</span> 比較<span style=\"color: red;\">高機率有警察</span><br />\n而唐賢街比較之下 <span style=\"color: red;\">路線較為迂迴同埋狹窄</span> <br />\n當中特別提醒既係 <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">至善街迴旋處係死路 唔好入</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z1LS61O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz1LS61O.jpg&h=cf265e57&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">唔好比遠處既知專學院個距離感呃左你</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n而唐賢街往調景嶺方向<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">有大量建築用料同埋路障</span></strong><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">小心佢地比唔好撠親 同埋唔好搞亂佢地</span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/51sFwuS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F51sFwuS.jpg&h=b805c65d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZbdtFoz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZbdtFoz.jpg&h=866c0807&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後附上調景嶺巴士站圖<br />\n雖然離開將軍澳區就已經安全 但係都係比大家參考下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zshY2DF.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzshY2DF.png&h=3a62f761&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aa97c4fdd4a3fbfc0ba6ac68fa6e5832e79249ca","tid":1403944,"uid":240278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:23:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71dce86f1ff4ddbe8b7e4fde1de1d8039dbffaa1","tid":1403944,"uid":14274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:27:13.000Z","msg":"推<br />\nbe warer"},{"pid":"7b302dc5c8498385b9e4ad6341a3659cab4c97c6","tid":1403944,"uid":32655,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:37:04.000Z","msg":"非《一次又一次難清場》<br />\n是《一次又一次難拉人》"},{"pid":"51fd92b58f9f911af88bf4b88b2924e6d774de0c","tid":1403944,"uid":21887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:38:41.000Z","msg":"push<br />\n<br />\n<code>8月5號全城罷工 8月5號全城罷工 8月5號全城罷工 我無嘢講 我要見律師 我要去醫院驗傷  我唔會解鎖電話 我唔會簽任何文件</code>"},{"pid":"531aa8fd43886544961abc72873929a0d96cd9f2","tid":1403944,"uid":70888,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:38:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"baf57a2c5d56c52e5c73d7ddc7367a29f88db8b2","tid":1403944,"uid":240278,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:39:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">翠林方向</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/fWrKYkg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FfWrKYkg.jpg&h=2959dbf7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n翠林係寶林北路果邊<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">如果你要由將軍澳翻去<br />\n可能就要行翻去寶林</span><br />\n加上<span style=\"color: red;\">翠林係一條山路</span> 所以<span style=\"color: red;\">消耗既體力都唔少</span><br />\n呢一點要注意<br />\n<br />\n但係如果你行翠林呢條路既話<br />\n可以<span style=\"color: red;\">直接徒步行到寶達、秀茂坪 相對路線黎講比較簡單</span><br />\n<br />\n加上<span style=\"color: red;\">寶林有新都城三個商場做掩護</span>，可以係入面換衫<br />\n只係<span style=\"color: red;\">呢條路線同警署比較近</span> 可能會有比較多警車<br />\n<br />\n最後 如果唔係區內人 <span style=\"color: red;\">建議撤退既時候盡量唔好入寶林邨</span> <br />\n因為邨內<span style=\"color: red;\">錯綜複雜 比較容易盪失路</span> 如果真係要入邨既話<br />\n新都城二期<span style=\"color: red;\">有出口係可以直接到寶林邨</span>內既寶林商場既"},{"pid":"8a7d8fda3497f2d4ef4f35982358e8e5beb88142","tid":1403944,"uid":276973,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:41:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/trrKV2e.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtrrKV2e.jpg&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvCHfnck7qU2fF1mVfqY7ZMk%3D&h=926883d4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/trrKV2e.jpg</a><br />\n<br />\n好似尋晚咁預演左場，一黎即閃，再配合好d，前線必需互通"},{"pid":"ee0e3140d77323c7fa2aa076eea482a5b406f5c9","tid":1403944,"uid":1482,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:45:30.000Z","msg":"提醒大家 今日係全港運動日 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9613eb0d5044aa823db3e0242a48f432f0cecb0","tid":1403944,"uid":240278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:50:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"485c52ff33d89190db03e8ca65364322afc01d6f","tid":1403944,"uid":259010,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:54:58.000Z","msg":"出TKO 要過山 無MTR + road block 己經收你皮<br />\n<br />\n行山友<br />\n全部都係上山路段<br />\n科大路線<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2S3EF7a.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2S3EF7a.png&h=d7c64ce0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tL7idBq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtL7idBq.png&h=ff6dc17b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n觀塘路線<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VKGu3mA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVKGu3mA.png&h=adff2f90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wXZDX25.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwXZDX25.png&h=23fceaae&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n油塘 晒草灣 路線<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cw5WJpr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCw5WJpr.png&h=983d5fd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5yOJpH5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5yOJpH5.jpg&h=6f94f819&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n康城路線 (唔建議  入面商場咩都無)<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AQTpTCB.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAQTpTCB.png&h=dd8eab55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jeKTMWs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjeKTMWs.png&h=b32b0bbd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n將軍澳D路都行人友善 好多天橋同行人隧道"},{"pid":"bbd13f48ac0570ba27ef2a478d50566e13c4af88","tid":1403944,"uid":240278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid